# Restream Chat++ — environment variable layout for OAuth credentials.
#
# At runtime, the app reads credentials from one of:
#   1. The RESTREAM_CLIENT_ID + RESTREAM_CLIENT_SECRET environment variables
#   2. The macOS Keychain entry under service "api.restream.io" (account=client_id,
#      password=client_secret)
#
# Register your Restream developer app at https://restream.io/settings/api,
# set the redirect URI to: http://localhost:8765/oauth, and grant the scopes:
#   profile.read, channels.read, stream.read, chat.read,
#   channels.write, stream.write
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill it in if you're not using Keychain.
# The .env / .env.local files are gitignored — never commit secrets.

RESTREAM_CLIENT_ID=
RESTREAM_CLIENT_SECRET=
